---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Bodhic AI">
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div style="color: var(--body); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px;">
            <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">1. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>At Bodhic AI, we collect minimal personal information to provide our services. This includes your name, email address, and authentication credentials when you sign up. We do not store your raw payment details; all transactions are processed securely by our payment gateway partners (e.g., Razorpay).</p>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">2. Google OAuth and Third-Party Login</h3>
            <p>If you choose to log in using Google (or other third-party identity providers), we request access to your basic profile information, specifically your <strong>email address</strong>, <strong>name</strong>, and <strong>profile picture</strong>. We use this data exclusively to authenticate your identity, create your user account on our platform, and display your avatar/username on your public profile. We do <strong>not</strong> request access to your Google Drive, Gmail, or any other private Google services, and we will never share or sell your Google profile data to third parties.</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <p>Your information is used solely to provide, maintain, and improve the Bodhic AI marketplace. This includes facilitating transactions between buyers and sellers, sending transactional emails, and ensuring the security of our platform.</p>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">4. Data Security</h3>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. Our platform strictly adheres to standard compliance frameworks to prevent unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your data.</p>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--ink); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">5. Contact Us</h3>
            <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to request data deletion, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@bodhicai.tech?subject=Privacy%20Data%20Request" style="color: var(--primary);">support@bodhicai.tech</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
